      <title>日本公司从美国到韩国对阿里巴巴发起专利诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/japanese-firm-hits-alibaba-with-patent-lawsuits-from-us-to-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家鲜为人知的日本公司在三个国家起诉阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司，指控其侵犯其跨境电子商务专利，寻求法院针对这家中国网络先驱发布禁令或赔偿损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/japanese-firm-hits-alibaba-with-patent-lawsuits-from-us-to-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿里巴巴首席执行官因增长放缓而更换电子商务主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/alibaba-s-ceo-replaces-e-commerce-chief-as-growth-falters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司首席执行官埃迪·吴(Eddie Wu)将接管该公司的核心电子商务业务，取代该公司最有经验的高管之一，掌管中国最大的在线市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/alibaba-s-ceo-replaces-e-commerce-chief-as-growth-falters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 02:01:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能增添乐观情绪，联想60%的涨势可能会延续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/lenovo-s-60-rally-may-extend-as-ai-adds-to-optimism-tech-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球个人电脑需求复苏的迹象以及人们对联想集团人工智能相关产品的热情，联想集团股价连续三个月的上涨可能会持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/lenovo-s-60-rally-may-extend-as-ai-adds-to-optimism-tech-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将资助双向充电技术将电动汽车转变为发电厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/uk-to-fund-bidirectional-technology-to-turn-evs-into-power-plants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国正在为双向充电技术的开发提供资金，该技术可以将电动汽车转变为备用电源，并帮助该国实现其气候目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/uk-to-fund-bidirectional-technology-to-turn-evs-into-power-plants</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顶级新兴市场基金为Forsaken中国股票带来新面貌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/a-top-us-emerging-markets-fund-increases-china-exposure-focusing-on-valuation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家总部位于纽约的新兴市场股票基金的表现优于大多数同行，近几个月来一直在增持中国股票，因为该基金认为今年的无情抛售有些过度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/a-top-us-emerging-markets-fund-increases-china-exposure-focusing-on-valuation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 00:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国收回重拳以确保昂贵的电动汽车继续流向欧盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/china-is-under-pressure-to-keep-exporting-electric-cars-to-the-eu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当欧盟对中国对电动汽车的支持发起调查时，欧盟的汽车制造商准备迎接这个日益自信的超级大国的痛苦报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/china-is-under-pressure-to-keep-exporting-electric-cars-to-the-eu</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>景顺中国首席信息官预计明年股价将实现两位数反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/invesco-s-china-cio-eyes-double-digit-stock-rebound-next-year-on-economy-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[景顺有限公司香港和中国首席投资官表示，在国内经济复苏迹象和更多政策支持的支撑下，MSCI中国指数可能在2024年上涨10%以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/invesco-s-china-cio-eyes-double-digit-stock-rebound-next-year-on-economy-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rite Aid 在滥用人工智能面部识别后被 FTC 禁止使用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/rite-aid-banned-from-ai-facial-recognition-by-ftc-after-misuse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为与美国联邦贸易委员会达成的隐私和解协议的一部分，Rite Aid Corp. 必须在未来五年内停止使用面部识别技术，该委员会表示，该药房连锁店滥用该技术，错误地将消费者标记为商店扒手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/rite-aid-banned-from-ai-facial-recognition-by-ftc-after-misuse</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 22:04:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
